OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773781557
OL,3,C'Significant new information' in quest
OL,4,Cto identify body found in Powys
OL,5,Creservoir
OL,7,FDetectives attempting to identify the
OL,8,Fbody of a mystery man found dead
OL,9,Fwearing a wetsuit in a Powys reservoir
OL,10,Fsay they have received "a significant
OL,11,Fnumber" of reports following a fresh
OL,12,Fappeal.
OL,14,FThe man's body was found by a walker
OL,15,Fat Claerwen Reservoir, Powys, in
OL,16,FOctober 2024, and is thought to have
OL,17,Fbeen in the water for up to 12 weeks
OL,18,Fbefore its discovery.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
