PN,46502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773781557
OL,3,C'Significant new information' in quest
OL,4,Cto identify body found in Powys
OL,5,Creservoir
OL,7,FLast week, Dyfed Powys Police issued
OL,8,Fan image recreating the man's face in
OL,9,Fthe hope members of the public would
OL,10,Fbe able to confirm his identity.
OL,12,FPolice says the man was aged between
OL,13,F30 and 60, around 6ft (1.83m),
OL,14,Fweighing between 202lbs and 220lbs
OL,15,F(91.5kg - 99.5kg), and of white
OL,16,FEuropean descent.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773781557
OL,3,C'Significant new information' in quest
OL,4,Cto identify body found in Powys
OL,5,Creservoir
OL,7,FHe was found wearing an extra large
OL,8,FZone 3 Agile wetsuit, and despite
OL,9,Fsearches around the reservoir from the
OL,10,Fland and water, no other personal
OL,11,Fbelongings were recovered.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Anthea Ponting
OL,14,Fsays the calls range from "specific
OL,15,Fnames of individuals" to "more
OL,16,Fambiguous reports", and said the force
OL,17,Fis looking at each of them in detail.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
