PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773781557
OL,3,C'Significant new information' in quest
OL,4,Cto identify body found in Powys
OL,5,Creservoir
OL,7,FShe added: "We have carried out a wide
OL,8,Frange of enquiries over the past 16
OL,9,Fmonths, which began with working with
OL,10,Fneighbouring police forces to conduct
OL,11,Fchecks for missing or wanted people
OL,12,Fwho have not been traced, before
OL,13,Fextending our enquiries to contact all
OL,14,FUK forces.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
