PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1773781557
OL,3,C'Significant new information' in quest
OL,4,Cto identify body found in Powys
OL,5,Creservoir
OL,7,F"We have run searches through the
OL,8,FPolice National Database, issued
OL,9,Fbulletins to police overseas through
OL,10,FInterpol, searched DNA, fingerprint
OL,11,Fand dental records for potential
OL,12,Fmatches, and issued public and media
OL,13,Fappeals for information.
OL,15,F"Each time we have reached out to the
OL,16,Fpublic, we've been provided with some
OL,17,Flines of enquiry to follow-up on, but
OL,18,Funfortunately none have yet proven to
OL,19,Fbe the key to finding out who this
OL,20,Fperson is.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
